{"tid":2180694,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[AN/IOS]有冇人有玩新出果隻Tom and Jerry: Chase","createTime":"2020-08-30T05:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T14:31:49.000Z","uid":225696,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"44f70f677684c86380e7d7610917b0471467593b","tid":2180694,"uid":225696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T05:00:30.000Z","msg":"玩法:一個做貓，4個做老鼠，類似兵捉賊<br />\n貓同老鼠、唔同角色、唔同SKIN都有唔同技能，技能係玩果時達成某D條件升LV就可以用<br />\n<br />\n偵察階段:<br />\n貓:放陷阱+打機械老鼠<br />\n老鼠:偵查芝士位置+食EXP蛋糕，同要守住蛋糕<br />\n<br />\n正式階段:<br />\n一隻貓捉老鼠，捉到3隻(每隻都要守到成功用火箭殺左先算捉到)就贏<br />\n4個做老鼠分工偷芝士到指定位置，然後逃走<br />\n<br />\n明明做老鼠個勝利條件難咁多，貓又愈後愈勁，但唔知點解冇人肯做貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLINK自己上APP STORE搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2bb4bbe039cf2b1bda0b2a9e6de4ac9f88980b","tid":2180694,"uid":61721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T05:39:19.000Z","msg":"支那仔玩支那驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772500e7921b68a228179eb81e76befc12429e0d","tid":2180694,"uid":225696,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"cd2bb4bbe039cf2b1bda0b2a9e6de4ac9f88980b","tid":2180694,"uid":61721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T05:39:19.000Z","msg":"支那仔玩支那驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:21:42.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong NetEase Interactive Entertainment Limited"},{"pid":"e460316a01466e151163fbaf88ca9f9d6a1cae85","tid":2180694,"uid":367155,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"條友真係唔識㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3e18f8f9a12efba549b98ab7669536f0105c82","tid":2180694,"uid":61721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"772500e7921b68a228179eb81e76befc12429e0d","tid":2180694,"uid":225696,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"qu